    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/66bd8af5d07658f40fb00977d8e6c22e.poster.avif?t=1769783395\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/66bd8af5d07658f40fb00977d8e6c22e.webm?t=1769783395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/66bd8af5d07658f40fb00977d8e6c22e.mp4?t=1769783395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉剑和斧头吧。这里的战斗发生在英雄们的心灵中：可爱的和尚和老人们只有一个目标：冥想！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但这不会容易。压力、账单、心碎和其他敌人将试图打扰我们的英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/c77a7890d03476fa2ff1f699a0dababc.poster.avif?t=1769783395\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/c77a7890d03476fa2ff1f699a0dababc.webm?t=1769783395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/c77a7890d03476fa2ff1f699a0dababc.mp4?t=1769783395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的武器是音乐！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建一套由部件组成的卡组，阻止敌人扰乱僧侣的宁静。<br>获得 XP 和金币，收集遗物并提升你的力量。演奏你的乐器，在每个关卡中击败所有敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里有大量手绘场景！想要到达终点，需要巧妙地组合合适的部件与遗物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种独特的遗物<br>数十种不同的部件<br>4 位独特角色（仍在增加），每位都演奏不同的乐器<br>数十种试图打扰僧侣的敌人<br>专为游戏创作的原创配乐<br>所有美术均由专业插画师手绘完成 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/c990c011baa71ef5a9eb6a3c015f6d1b.poster.avif?t=1769783395\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/c990c011baa71ef5a9eb6a3c015f6d1b.webm?t=1769783395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189950/extras/c990c011baa71ef5a9eb6a3c015f6d1b.mp4?t=1769783395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
